#: src/getbar.c:883
msgid ""
"Usage: getbar [OPTION]... URL\n"
"Download URL with HTTP(S) GET and record throughput bars.\n"
msgstr ""
"Utilisation : getbar [OPTION]... URL\n"
"Telecharge l'URL par HTTP(S) GET et enregistre des barres de debit.\n"

#: src/getbar.c:888
msgid "split by received block size\n"
msgstr "diviser par taille de bloc recu\n"

#: src/getbar.c:890
msgid "split by time interval (NUM may be fractional)\n"
msgstr "diviser par intervalle de temps (NUM peut etre fractionnaire)\n"

#: src/getbar.c:892
msgid "stop after receiving NUM bytes\n"
msgstr "arreter apres NUM octets recus\n"

#: src/getbar.c:894
msgid "stop after timeout\n"
msgstr "arreter apres delai\n"

#: src/getbar.c:896
msgid "output offset and polynomial coeffs\n"
msgstr "afficher decalage et coeffs polynomiaux\n"

#: src/getbar.c:898
msgid "render chart (.png/.svg/.pdf/.eps) or save script\n"
msgstr "rendre un graphique (.png/.svg/.pdf/.eps) ou sauver le script\n"

#: src/getbar.c:900
msgid "overwrite gnuplot output file\n"
msgstr "ecraser le fichier de sortie gnuplot\n"

#: src/getbar.c:902
msgid "output estimated bytes/sec after delay\n"
msgstr "afficher octets/s estimes apres delai\n"

#: src/getbar.c:904
msgid "print summary after series: count size duration bps\n"
msgstr "afficher le resume apres la serie : nombre taille duree bps\n"

#: src/getbar.c:906
msgid "omit pre-data wait from series, window, count; set -p offset\n"
msgstr "omettre l'attente pre-donnees de la serie, fenetre, comptage ; definir l'offset -p\n"

#: src/getbar.c:908
msgid "more logging to stderr\n"
msgstr "plus de journaux vers stderr\n"

#: src/getbar.c:910
msgid "omit the bar series on stdout\n"
msgstr "omettre la serie de barres sur stdout\n"

#: src/getbar.c:912
msgid "display this help and exit\n"
msgstr "afficher cette aide et quitter\n"

#: src/getbar.c:914
msgid "output version information and exit\n"
msgstr "afficher les informations de version et quitter\n"

#: src/getbar.c:916
msgid ""
"Block mode (-b) prints per-block durations in microseconds. By default\n"
"the first value is the wait before data arrives. With -d that wait is\n"
"omitted from the series and derived metrics; -p then reports the delay\n"
"as offset. Interval mode (-i) includes leading zero intervals by default;\n"
"with -d they are omitted and -p offset is the idle time in seconds.\n"
"Polynomial, count, and estimate lines are printed after the series.\n"
"Optional theming: $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/getbar/gnuplot.rc\n"
msgstr ""
"Le mode bloc (-b) affiche les durees par bloc en microsecondes. Par defaut, la premiere valeur est l'attente avant l'arrivee des donnees ; avec -d, cette attente est omise de la serie et des metriques derivees ; -p rapporte alors le delai comme offset. Le mode intervalle (-i) inclut par defaut des intervalles zero initiaux ; avec -d, ils sont omis et l'offset -p est le temps d'inactivite en secondes.\n"
"Les lignes polynome, comptage et estimation sont affichees apres la serie.\n"
"Theming optionnel : $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/getbar/gnuplot.rc\n"

